snippet.title: 【HoloCure】 September Update Trailer
snippet.description:
HoloCure's first major update comes September 9, 2022, with 9 new playable characters, an outfit selector, new stages, and more weapons, items, shop upgrades, and enemies! 

Source https://twitter.com/HoloCureGame/status/1561484560235302913

Controller support also confirmed: https://twitter.com/kaynimatic/status/1561490152010047488

And a new Gambler's Tears feature to allow for instant purchase of desired talents: https://twitter.com/HoloCureGame/status/1553221891849986048

Follow HoloCure at https://twitter.com/HoloCureGame

*This channel is not affiliated with the HoloCure development team*
